Titolo: Eternal Ring

Anno: 2000

Descrizione: Eternal Ring is a first-person action role-playing game  developed by FromSoftware and published in North America by Agetec. Released in 2000, it was a launch title for the PlayStation 2 in both Japan and North America. The game was made available via emulation for the PlayStation 4 in North America on May 23, 2017.